@startuml
actor User
participant BattlePage
participant InnPage
participant PvECampaign
participant HomePage
participant UserDAO
database DB

== Exit From Inn ==

User -> InnPage : Click Exit
activate InnPage
InnPage -> HomePage : return to menu
HomePage --> User : Home page shown
deactivate InnPage

== Save At Inn ==

InnPage -> PvECampaign : saveAtInnWithoutAdvancing() / completeInnRoomAndSave()
activate PvECampaign
PvECampaign -> UserDAO : updateProgress(profile)
activate UserDAO
UserDAO -> DB : UPDATE users SET party_level=?, room_count=?
activate DB
DB --> UserDAO : success
deactivate DB
deactivate UserDAO
deactivate PvECampaign

== Exit During Battle ==

User -> BattlePage : Close / exit battle
activate BattlePage
BattlePage --> User : Progress from mid-battle is not saved
BattlePage -> HomePage : return to menu
deactivate BattlePage
@enduml
